95
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:31,980
You just let the grown-ups worry about grown-up things, okay?

96
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:34,270
Your mom and dad

97
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:37,760
have our financial future all under control.

98
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,560
