100
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:48,550
Ah, the multi-family vacation.

101
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,120
Let's see who we've got.

102
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,270
The Van Houtens, of course. The Hibberts.

103
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,860
Superintendent Chalmers and his daughter.

104
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,990
